        void onSubscribe​(int result,

        Deprecated.
        subscriptions are no longer supported
        The subscribe action was successful. To subscribe to a feed, call Virtuoso.subscribe().
        Parameters:
        result - The result is one of the values from Common.BackplaneResult. 0 (SUCCESS) is guaranteed to indicate success.
        feedUuid - The UUID of the subscribed feed.

      • onSubscriptions

        void onSubscriptions​(int result,
                     String[] uuids)
        Deprecated.
        subscriptions are no longer supported
        Returns all subscriptions known to the server. To obtain all subscriptions, call Virtuoso.subscriptions().
        Parameters:
        result - A value from Common.BackplaneResult. 0 (SUCCESS) is guaranteed to indicate success.
        uuids - Array of all feeds that the user is subscribed to.
        See Also:
        Common.BackplaneResult
